{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d31cca4705","title":"给彭石麟的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"93f919c680","index":0,"year":1954,"month":3,"day":31,"articleId":"d31cca4705"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"91628913c9","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d31cca4705","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭石麟，大革命时期曾任湘潭县清溪乡女子职业学校校长。毛泽东在清溪乡一带从事革命活动时得到过他的帮助。"},{"id":"b470549a87","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d31cca4705","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛蕊珠，即毛宇居，毛泽东的堂兄和少年时的私垫老师。"},{"id":"e63e29626a","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d31cca4705","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李激清，毛泽东少年时的老师，大革命时期曾协助毛泽东在广州办过《政治周报》，建国后，曾任湖南省文史研究馆馆员。"},{"id":"3130a19550","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d31cca4705","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"文运昌，毛泽东的表兄。"}],"contents":[{"id":"1a1344d8b7","type":"title","text":"给彭石麟的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d31cca4705"},{"id":"91628913c9","type":"paragraph","text":"石腾先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d31cca4705"},{"id":"b470549a87","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五四年三月九日函示敬悉。尊事已托毛蕊珠兄，我的翰旋可以不必了。我不大愿意为乡里亲友形诸荐膜，间或也有，但极少。李渐清先生、文运昌兄，以此见托，我婉辞了，他们的问题是他们自己托人解决的。先生生计困难，可以告我，在费用方面，我再助先生若干，是不难的。此复，祈谅是幸。顺致敬意","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d31cca4705"},{"id":"e63e29626a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d31cca4705"},{"id":"3130a19550","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五四年三月三十一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d31cca4705"}],"page":{"id":"33e83058c2","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"d31cca4705","start":62,"end":62}}}},"__N_SSG":true}